{
  "stem": "3631.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we finally came to Bologna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, we were in a DP camp in Modena, which was about 30 miles north of Bologna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was a former military academy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed there from July-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] from July, 18, I think, to September 27th.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were about 4,000 Jews there and-- and some other nationals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a bad camp, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- these things-- you know, when we were liberated, we thought, well, the world would have understanding for us and would try to-- to help us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, they did, but there-- it was a great disappointment, the way we were being pushed around.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the camp, we were guarded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If we wanted to go out, we-- if we wanted to sell a shirt or something, go out sell it on the black market, we could not.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to-- they searched our-- they searched us, when we went out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sleeping was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It-- it wasn't very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a contingent of Greek Jews there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was-- it-- it-- it was unpleasant, and so we had to go on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we started-- my father and I started to-- to scout on our-- we went to Milan first, but conditions weren't much better there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went back to Modena.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went to Florence, and it was a little better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we finally decided to go to Rome, because we felt the potential in Rome was much better to-- to-- to get.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in Modena, I counted about 60 to 80 people on a stone floor, sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, people looking for their relatives.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it-- it was-- it was very, very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
